author: Chris Roberts
title: Trade Tested reviewed by Chris Roberts
text: I recently purchased a 3m x 3m gazebo from Trade Tested and have been very impressed with the product quality and service. A friend had purchased a similar one from a different retail outlet and had to return it because it was below par, being of inferior construction. Keep up the high standards!
